query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ab_test_daily_metrics` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `testId` int NOT NULL,
  `variantId` int NOT NULL,
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `impressions` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `clicks` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `spend` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.00,
  `sales` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.00,
  `orders` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `acos` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `roas` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ctr` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cvr` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `createdAt` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `idx_ab_test_daily_metrics_unique` (`testId`, `variantId`, `date`),
  KEY `idx_ab_test_daily_metrics_testId` (`testId`),
  KEY `idx_ab_test_daily_metrics_variantId` (`variantId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
